sentences.en: Elected to the County Council in 2004, he is a mayoral candidate for the 2008 election.

sentences.en: The mayoral nomination process has been increased by two times in recent weeks.

sentences.en: A valiant resistance sniper hunted down and killed two bloodthirsty fascist occupiers near the al Hurya base in the city of Karkook at 7.30 on Sunday 21 May 2006.

sentences.en: Indeed, the results of Do Thien Kinh et. al., that a further year of education reduces the probability of being in poverty by a mere two percentage points, suggests that the fallacy may apply.
